## Context

- Completed Phase 3-4 tasks (109, 110) and partial task 107 for innate immunity deficiency model
- Cross-project data from autoantibody-target-network-mapping and gas-molecular-mimicry-mapping became available, unblocking Phase 4
- Pipeline code in: src/pandas_pans/innate_immunity_deficiency_model/ (11 scripts total)
